definition.text: This command provides a mechanism to navigate to a Docs page or an anchor within the page.

paragraphs.text: docs.goto Project->Docs Page Category->Docs Page Name->Docs Page Anchor
Project: It's the project where the Node, Concept, Topic, Tutorial or Review is defined.
Docs Page Category: Node, Concept, Topic, Tutorial or Review.
Docs Page Name: For Nodes it is the type of node; for Concepts, the concept name; for Topics, the topic's page name, for Tutorials, the tutorial step name; for Reviews, the review page name.
Docs Page Anchor : This parameter is optional. If present, it refers to an Docs Anchor paragraph defined within the page.
